<L>__{interior oracle's chambers (matrix) day}
<A>__{it looks like a suburban tract house. there is a lot of cozy furniture, a dining roon hutch filled with china, shelves and tables crowded with doilies, knick knacks and ceramic brick a brack. neo follows the plastic carpet runner to the kitchen. a woman is huddled beside the oven, peering inside through the cracked door.}
<C>__{neo}
<D>__{hello?}
<C>__{oracle }
<D>__{i know. you're neo. be right with you.}
<C>__{neo}
<D>__{you're the oracle?}
