<D>__{i think so.}
<C>__{oracle}
<D>__{so? what do you think? you think you're the one?}
<C>__{neo}
<D>__{i don't know.}
<A>__{she gestures to a wooden plaque, the kind every grandma has, except that the words are in latin.}
<C>__{oracle}
<D>__{you know what that means? it's latin. means, 'know thyself.'}
<A>__{she puts her cigarette down.}
<C>__{oracle}
